name: Faye
description: There once was a family of fairies who lived in a cottage of trees. The fairies were somewhat peculiar, and came in a set of three. The sisters Faye, Ferne, and Fawn noticed one day their tree was gone. They moved to a new one not far away, and a set of three they decided to stay. This one is Faye's home, nestled high in the branches, the perfect spot for her wild fairy dances.
